<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #0d0f0b; color: #fff; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; overflow: hidden; }
        .container { text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 10; padding: 40px; }
        .bg-glow { position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); width: 600px; height: 600px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%); z-index: 1; }
        h1 { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 120px; margin: 0; color: #d4af37; letter-spacing: 20px; opacity: 0.8; }
        h2 { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 24px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 8px; margin-top: -20px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); }
        p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; margin: 30px 0; max-width: 400px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; line-height: 1.6; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 15px 40px; border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3); color: #d4af37; text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 4px; transition: all 0.4s ease; background: transparent; }
        .btn:hover { background: #d4af37; color: #0d0f0b; box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2); }
        .logo { height: 60px; margin-bottom: 40px; opacity: 0.8; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg-glow"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://theatlantichorizon.ie/images/Logo.png" alt="Manor Logo" class="logo">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Sanctuary Not Found</h2>
        <p>The path you seek within the Manor grounds does not exist, or has been relocated to preserve the privacy of our guests.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn">Return to Grounds</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
